{"tid":1306444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【上水】內地人可以個人遊漏洞無限次來港　","createTime":"2019-07-11T07:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T07:55:13.000Z","uid":86592,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef8030076bfeb4884cc48d7623c1dbacbab4117f","tid":1306444,"uid":86592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:00:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355026&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852wfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=22c498bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355026&h=bef27b34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355026</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】民主黨發現有內地人利用「個人遊」簽注漏洞無限次來港，促請保安局與內地商討堵塞漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨年初收到入境處前線人員投訴，有內地人利用「個人遊」一星期內多次來港，懷疑他們走水貨及從事其他非法活動。<br />\n<br />\n個人遊簽注分為四種，分別為三個月一次、三個月兩次、一年一次以及一年兩次，使用完畢可以續簽。民主黨上月在內地口岸發現設有自助簽注機，三分鐘就可以完成續簽。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員林卓廷曾向保安局查詢，保安局只強調「個人遊」簽注申請相隔時間沒有限制，林卓廷批評簽注漏洞，令一周一行形同虛設。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷要求保安局盡快與內地公安機關商討，限制內地居民以個人遊或團隊旅遊簽注，一年最多只可來港八次。"},{"pid":"6abe9c60610a5e6b912894bb5bc2500eecb72736","tid":1306444,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://res.dotdotnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/law_20171016_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.dotdotnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Flaw_20171016_590.jpg&h=d7a19961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又多一個理由填補法例漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea7ea4af9623766b420272c03b6b788f51802f8","tid":1306444,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"唔好煩，1月1行啦"},{"pid":"8eba131a713c1a1cf72202d707fdf1a08d594954","tid":1306444,"uid":86592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{